content: Become master of time, space, mind, soul, reality, and the power of the multiverse with the Infinity Gauntlet. Custom made to order, this brass and genuine leather glove provides a comfortable fit and comes adorned with each of the 6 Infinity Stones.

Add some class to your look by toting around your things inside this Tropaeis leather khaki messenger bag. This handmade genuine leather bag comes with ample storage space with room for everything from your books and laptop to your smartphone.

Convert friends and family into LEGO form using this personalized 3D printing service. Simply submit two photos of the recipient – and their likeness will be eerily recreated onto a 15mm head using sophisticated full-color 3D printers.

Avoid becoming a tasty morsel in the post-apocalyptic world with a little help from this zombie repellent soap. This handmade soap contains a mixture of special and soothing ingredients like coconut and palm oil that nurture the skin and will mask your scent to the undead.

Satisfy your sweet tooth and morbid sense of humor simultaneously with the anatomically correct chocolate skull. Hand crafted with a jaw-dropping level of realism, this Belgian chocolate delight will awe and intrigue every gluttonous onlooker.

Make an already special event unforgettable by creating a surreal nighttime setting using these string fairy lights. These quality LEDs light up the sky with a soft warm glow that creates an intimate environment ideal for weddings and other celebrations.

Slippers have finally become a manly thing to wear thanks to these Panzer tank slippers. The tank slippers will warm your feet feet while ruggedly armoring them with two inches of thick padding, giving you an ominous look that will strike fear in those who stand in your way.

Give others a peek at your inner beauty as you turn heads wearing this x-ray skeleton bodysuit. Made from top quality four-way stretch Lycra, it provides a superbly comfortable fit to transform your body into a giant x-ray of yourself.

Let your young artist know how much they mean to you by surprising them with their very own personalized crayon set. The name of your choosing is crafted from recycled crayons – giving each letter its own unique and vibrant color scheme.

Look like you just arrived from a war-torn futuristic world by applying this Terminator robotic prosthetic over your eye. This handmade piece is modeled after the iconic T-800 terminators and crafted from silicone to ensure a comfortable fit.

Give your sci-fi inspired costume a “wow” factor with this biomechanical spinal armor. This incredible custom piece is available in sizes ranging from small to large, and can be customized with your choice of light color to create a truly unique look.

Anyone can have a studio photo hanging in their home, separate yourself from the bunch by immortalizing your loved ones with one of these personalized Etch A Sketch portraits. Simply submit your favorite picture and you will receive your own unique portrait.

Add some out-of-this-word color to any outfit by topping it off with these amazing galaxy combat boots. These custom boots are hand painted with an incredible flurry of colors that combine to form an intergalactic landscape that envelops every square inch of the boots.

Bring some geeky style to your bedroom or game room by decorating with these gamer-approved NES cartridge pillows. Each pillow is expertly styled to resemble the vintage and bulky grey NES cartridges – right down to the pixelated artwork.

Stay nice and toasty on a chilly winter night by snuggling up with this chunky knit blanket. Each blanket is handmade from lush 100% merino wool and is available in sizes that range from 15 x 23 inches to 70 x 78 inches.

Avoid falling into a culinary rut by keeping your recipes fresh and diverse using these foodie dice. The set includes laser engraved wooden dice that display various spices and ingredients designed to make you more adventurous in your cooking endeavors.

Project a plethora of lively colors onto the walls of your home by lighting the room with the rainbow mood light. This customized light bulb comes painted with a lovely rainbow design that creates instant murals on your plain walls as soon as the light comes on.

titleEN: The Great Wave Off Kanagawa Mural
content: Spice up your home’s decor with a little color and Asian flair with this wall mural depicting The Great Wave off Kanagawa. This massive 66″ x 96″ removable mural perfectly depicts Japanese artist Hokusai’s iconic nineteenth century masterpiece.

Give your soak a fun Millennial twist by dropping in one or two of these Tide Pod bath bombs into your tub. They’re styled like the oh-so-tasty Tide Pods that are all the rage among the generation that says “yes we can!” to eating toxic chemicals for fleeting internet fame.

Bring some style to the way you tell time by strapping on this nixie tube wrist watch. This unique model features a sturdy body milled from a single piece of titanium complete with four z5900m Nixie tubes and a built-in accelerometer.

Add a unique aesthetic to your music listening experience by placing your vinyl on the Audiowood Barky turntable. This high quality turntable is crafted using a round slab of ash that is available in either a 115V or 230V versions.

Show off your love of fine music wherever you go by toting around this violin backpack. This custom handmade felt backpack is styled just like a violin and comes with an interior pocket, zippered closure, and an adjustable shoulder strap.

Turn your protruding belly into the highlight of your outfit with this “don’t eat watermelon seeds” shirt. This humorous garment is available in styles ranging from slouchy tanks to unisex sweatshirts – each of which display the comical quip in bold black letters.

Morph yourself into a prehistoric beast by slipping inside the walking dinosaur costume. Sparing no expense, this incredibly detailed and realistic costume depicts the mighty Tyrannosaurus Rex in a scaled down yet remarkably life like outfit.

Every wondered what house you would fall into if you were to attend Hogwarts? Well wonder no more with the Harry Potter sorting hat candle. Upon being lit, this eco-friendly soy wax candle begins to take in your aura and essence to reveal your ideal house as it begins to melt.

Put a big old smile on your favorite puzzle lover’s face by surprising them with a puzzle personalized with their very own face! The photograph of your choice will be transformed into a one of a kind 500 piece puzzle that measures around 16″ x 20″.

Give your humble abode a real wine lover’s touch by decorating your living room with this grape vine coffee table. Each table is crafted out of 100% recycled grape vines from California’s iconic Napa Valley region and is accented with a sleek glass top.

titleEN: Back To The Future Knitted Slippers
content: Display the latest futuristic fashion trends while you lounge around the house in these Back To The Future knitted slippers. Handmade from organic yarn, these extremely comfy slippers are styled to look exactly like Marty McFly’s 2015 Nike sneakers.

Experience what it’s like to be a mythical creature of the sea when you slip into a pair of these eye-catching mermaid leggings. Handmade from spandex fabric, they contour to your body for ultimate comfort and come in one of three vibrant hues.

If you’re a fan of pizza and long relaxing soaks, you’ll go wild for this pizza bath bomb. Upon making contact with the water, this mouth-watering slice begins to unleash an irresistible pizza scent along with a flurry of vibrant colors that will magically transform the water in your tub!

The loveable lawn gnomes have been infected and turned into the walking dead – now no lawn is safe from the growing army of zombie lawn gnomes. Here we see three gnomes brutally devouring a pink flamingo who will soon reanimate as the undead!

See what the world of your favorite series would look like if it was part of the modern world with this Game Of Thrones Google Maps poster. Illustrating Westeros like never before, it showcases nearly every town, castle, and fortress – from Flea Bottom to Pentos.

Isn’t it about time you started making some sound financial investments? So act now and drop your life savings on as many of these Bitcoin mining rigs as you can afford! You’ll be on the fast track to riches in the new and exciting world of magic internet money!

Give your humble abode an inviting coffee house vibe by lighting up this scented coffee beans candle. This fourteen ounce candle is handmade from 100% soy wax along with a delightful coffee fragrance oil and real dark roasted coffee-beans to produce an authentic smell.

Put those matches you have laying around your home to good use by firing them with the Magnum Mini matchstick crossbow. This handcrafted micro weapon is capable of launching straight wooden matches or Q-tips at distances over 50 feet.

Keep your inquisitive toddler occupied without needing a TV or tablet by having them play on the Busy Board. This handmade wooden toy measures 16 x 32 inches and is littered with fun and educational games and widgets for your little one to interact with.

titleEN: Custom LEGO Model Of Your Home
content: Immortalize your humble abode like never before by owning your very own custom LEGO model of your home. Simply submit pictures of your pad and Etsy shop Little Brick Lane will create an insanely detailed miniature of your house made entirely out of LEGOs.

Give your game room a touch of post-apocalyptic flair by creating some ambient lighting with this Fallout 4 Nuka Cola bottle light. Each bottle features game-accurate detailing, a real vinyl glossy label, and emits a cool blue glow.

Become the living embodiment of the Caped Crusader by suiting up in this Arkham City Batman bodysuit. Modeled after the iconic video game, it features a black and grey color scheme and is custom made from an athletic grade 4 way stretch material.

Stay ready for any threat headed your way by keeping your arsenal concealed in this firearm cabinet table. This unique wooden piece features a discreet trap door that opens up at the center to reveal an ample storage spot for all your guns.

Immortalize one the world’s greatest thespian’s likeness on virtually any surface using this Nicolas Cage face stamp. Crafted from rubber and wood, it features a laser-etched image of Mr. Cage’s million dollar smile so that you can share it with the world.

Give your bedroom a calming atmosphere when the lights go off by turning on this cloud night light. Each light is carefully hand made from hypoallergenic and antibacterial fibers that hold their shape to create an amazing and soothing visual when illuminated.

If traditional gold and silver bands aren’t your thing, you need to check out these gorgeous wooden wedding rings. Each brilliant ring is handcrafted using real 24K gold, wood, flowers, moss, and .925 silver flakes to create a truly unique band ideal for nature lovers.

Kick up your bedroom’s weirdness factor a notch or two by creating some accent lighting with one of these Beetlejuice lamps. These eye-catching whimsical lamps are based on the iconic character’s impossible to miss back and white striped suit.

Become the living embodiment of the Kingslayer – minus the chopped off hand – by dressing up in this Jamie Lannister cosplay armor. It’s skillfully crafted from high density EVA foam and is accented with real leather scales for a convincingly authentic look and feel.

Create an abundance of storage for your things with relatively little space using honeycomb shelving. These wooden shelves are expertly cut into hexagon shapes that create a practical honeycomb when placed side by side – making it both aesthetic and functional.

As far as beer carrying vessels go, these hand carved drinking horns are fit for the gods. They hold around 46 ounces of your favorite brew and are masterfully carved from a single Stag horn with intricate designs based on old Norse mythology.

Avoid misplacing your EDC by placing them on the everyday carry organizational rack. Handmade from Baltic birch wood, this compact rack assembles in mere seconds and provides a handy place for everything from your wallet and keys, to your watch and smartphone.

Combine your love of fine literature and gaming by creating your very own Final Fantasy bookmark. With this gamer approved gem you’ll be able to save your place in any book you’re reading almost the same way you save your progress while gaming!

Make your furry friend’s nights a little more comfortable by bundling him up in these dog pajamas. These canine jammies are designed to provide a comfortable fit and are available in various fun and vibrant patterns and designs.

Give the world a big ol’ “f**k you” by creating some quaint ambient lighting with this middle finger candle. It is skillfully handcrafted with the shape and size of an adult hand, with the wick located at the tip of the middle finger so that you can watch the negativity burn away.

titleEN: Star Wars Sarlacc Pit Baby Lounger Pillow
content: Keep your newborn in total comfort by feeding him to the insatiable Sarlacc. This Star Wars Sarlacc pit baby lounger pillow measures 36 inches all around, has a low pile minky top with a kona cotton bottom for utmost comfort, along with 2 nylon webbing handles.

Go from common man to king of the forest by slipping into this realistic grizzly bear costume. Each imposing grizzly getup is handmade to order to ensure a perfect fit and boasts features such as a padded body, a highly detailed tail, and paws and feet with realistic claws.

Help keep weekly stress levels at an all time low by creating a serene environment with this “stress be gone” candle. It’s handmade with a unique blend of herbs like chamomile, lavender, and other flowers that fill the air with a rich scent that will melt away your cares.

Take your fur baby with you wherever you go – even if pets aren’t allowed – by toting around this personalized miniature of your pet. Each custom sculpture is handcrafted from wool, wire, luxury fibers, and a cute clay nose to make your pet more adorable than ever.

Welcome to the exciting world of Plumbus ownership! A Plumbus will aid in many things in life, making life easier. With proper maintenance, handling, storage, and urging, Plumbus will provide you with a lifetime of better living and happiness.

Hold a piece of our nation’s history in the palm of your hand by acquiring this set of vintage rare coins. The set comes with coins from the late 19th and early 20th century like the Buffalo nickel, the Indian Head penny, the Barber dime, and the Mercury dime.

Reward your hard work – even if you came up just a little bit short – with this “I tried” gold star pin. You may not have come in first or at the top of your class, but that doesn’t mean your time and effort shouldn’t be recognized.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Star Stickers
content: Marvel at a starry sky 365 days a year by decorating your bedroom’s ceiling with these glow in the dark star stickers. They’re available in packs ranging from 200 to 1000 stars that each give off a bright white glow that transforms the area into a shimmering night sky.

Give your living room some industrial flair by lighting it up using this shadow box Edison lamp. The elegant frame is handcrafted from rich walnut and complemented by a vintage Edison filament bulb that gives off a warm, inviting glow.

Instantly liven up a drab wall by hanging some melted crayon art. An entire box of crayons is laid out over a white canvas to create a visually stunning piece that pleases the senses while giving the room some nostalgically artistic life.

Create a scene straight out of Jurassic Park in your very own home by decorating your room with this realistic wall bursting T-Rex. Made with a stunning level of detail and artistry, this fearsome predator will jump out at you with his ferocious jaws.

The cold will be no match for you with this insanely comfy soopascarf oversized scarf. Handmade from ultra soft yarn, this giant garment measures nine inches wide and seven feet long so that you can wrap it around your cold body any way you’d like.

Show off your love of American muscle – even when you’re not on the road – by decorating your living room or man cave with this 1966 Ford Mustang couch. Both pieces in the set are crafted from the actual front and rear ends of the classic 1966 Mustang.

Give your plain home some personality by turning your staircase into a distinguished library using these classic book stair decals. They’re made from vinyl and can be customized with virtually any book title you wish, giving you endless possibilities.

Thanks to this pixelated wooden travel chess set, your favorite strategy game is now more portable than ever. Each of the thin laser-cut pieces comes with a small notch at the bottom so that you can easily prop them up on the specially designed fold-out table.

The anatomically correct heart necklace is an awesome twist on the most popular necklace ever – the heart shape. Now you can show that special someone how much you love them by giving them your heart – literally – with this anatomically correct heart pendant necklace.

Dave Pollot has a unique passion turned business – he finds discarded thrift shop paintings and alters them with a geeky twist. Each masterpiece features different pop-culture references such as Star Wars, Doctor Who, Mario Bros, and many others.

Can’t decide what to drink tonight? No problem – just let the mixology dice choose for you! Each side of these wooden die contains a different ingredient that you can combine with other dice to come up with tasty new drinks that’ll thrill the palette and punish the liver.

Add some prehistoric flair to any part of your home with this charming Stegosaurus planter. This quaint little dinosaur planter takes the form of a small three inch tall and seven inch wide stegosaurus with a lively green plant growing out from its back.

Create an inviting atmosphere without having your bachelor pad smell like Bath And Body Works by lighting up some of these man approved scented candles. Each soy wax candle features a strong masculine scent like “cedar”, “campfire”, or “hunting lodge”.

titleEN: I Like Big Books Decorative Set
content: Show off your fondness for meaty books and catchy ’90s hip hop tunes by placing these “I like big books” decorative set on your shelf. The witty quip is a play on Sir Mix-A-Lot’s incredibly popular 1992 song “Baby Got Back”.

Add some eye-catching beauty to the way you fidget by trading up to the Vortex Dome. This focus/fidget toy features a large curved base that lets you spin this gorgeous dome round and round and admire the incredible turquoise color.

Create a serene dreamlike environment for your children with this light up cloud lamp. Handmade from natural hypoallergenic fibers, it’s shaped like a puffy cumulus cloud that takes on a brooding stormy appearance when lit.

Show off your clan’s humorous side by immortalizing everyone with a personalized Simpsons family portrait. Simply send in a quality picture of your family and in less than a week you will receive a personalized portrait of your family on the iconic Simpsons couch.

Take an interior decorating cue from Mother Nature herself by illuminating your home with this tree roots ceiling lamp. This work of art features a pewter wire design resembling an interconnected web of roots with light bulbs scattered all throughout the structure.

Thanks to this mini flip cup board everyone’s favorite party game is now more portable than ever! This low-volume version of the original employs a series of small finger flippers which are used to shoot mini versions of the iconic red party cups onto their tops.

Make your Jedi or Sith cosplay more authentic than ever by topping it off with one of these Star Wars illuminated lightsabers. Each lightsaber features an 11.4 inch long hilt that allows it to be wielded comfortably an can be customized with 1 of 6 alluring colors.

Increase your chances of survival if you’re ever in a life-threatening situation while in the wild by making sure to pack this credit card survival spear. This stainless steel card can easily be taken apart and put together to form a full sized broad head spear tip that is ideal for hunting.

Make a special occasion truly memorable by commemorating it using one of these personalized wood photos. The photograph of your choosing is transferred onto a lovely basswood slab so that your special memory remains with you forever.

For your birthday I got you the best and most expensive birthday card ever made. I give the best birthday cards – believe me. Nobody gives better birthday cards than me. You will never find a better present than this birthday card right here. And Mexico paid for it!

Add some natural flair to the way you store your literary collection by displaying them on this elm tree bookshelf. This unique tree of knowledge is handmade from elm and comes with an array of branches which are ideal for storing all kinds of reading material.

titleEN: National Parks Scratch Off Travel Map
content: Keeping track of all your adventures is easier and more fun than ever with this national parks scratch off travel map. Each of our nation’s 59 national parks – from Acadia to Zion national park – are covered in gold foil and ready to be scratched off once you visit them.

Set up an impromptu work station virtually anywhere using this portable wooden standing laptop desk. This hand crafted birch wood desk can support up to 50 lbs, will accommodate any laptop larger than 13″, and comes with an adjustable keyboard tray.

Get your little buccaneers excited about going to bed by docking this pirate ship bed in their bedroom. This extravagant bed features intricate detailing like a full mast equipped with a raggedy sail and even comes with a little slide next to the ship.

Give your fellow gamers a geeky greeting by placing this NES controller doormat in front of your front door. It’s styled like the iconic rectangular grey, black, and red controller and is weatherproof – making it great for indoor or outdoor use.

Stay warm on cold days by slipping into this insanely comfy turtleneck sleeping bag. This chunky bag is handmade from 100% merino sheep wool and designed with an extremely soft and snug turtleneck to keep the heat from escaping.

Enjoy all the best games from gaming’s golden age by inserting this 143 in 1 game cartridge into your original NES console. It comes packed with classics like Super Mario Bros. 1, 2, and 3, The Legend Of Zelda, and Bomberman 1 and 2.

Give the gift of soothing relaxation to your stressed out significant other by surprising them with this bath bomb gift box. The set comes with a dozen colorful handmade bombs made using natural ingredients like olive oil, coconut oil, and cocoa and shae butter.

Ensure you don’t spill a single drop of wine next time you’re drinking alfresco by bringing along this outdoor wine table. Its clever design can accommodate two glasses, a wine bottle, and still leave you enough room for a small plate or snack.

Give your bedroom a true Imperial touch by setting off an explosion of light using this Death Star lamp. When you flick it on, the light will shine through the small openings of this pint-sized Death Star to create brilliant 360 degree accent lighting.

Teach your children the invasive surveillance capabilities of good ‘ol Saint Nick by decorating your lush tree with the spy cam Christmas tree ornament. It creates the illusion that Santa is watching over your home to ensure that your kids behave and stay off the naughty list.

Make your nightly bonfire the most entertaining part of any camping trip using these sword campfire roasters. The set includes five stainless steel roasters designed like different sword hilts – ranging from civil war era swords to sci-fi inspired lightsabers.

Let your ride or die know she’ll always be number one in your heart with this “my favorite bitch” bff mug. These hilarious ceramic mugs are available in either an 11 ounce or 15 ounce size and can be personalized with the name of your choosing.

You’ve never truly experienced the greatness of pizza until you’ve slept in it. Perfect for kid’s sleep overs, these hand made comfy pizza slice sleeping bags can be custom ordered with your choice of toppings that comes either as extra pillows or as fixed blanket decorations.

Put your origami skills to the ultimate test by constructing this DIY giant 3D papercraft whale. This digital template will guide you through the steps necessary to transform lifeless paper into this mammoth whale that measures 39 inches tall.

What better way to show your beloved how much they mean to you than with one of these personalized pallet photos. The photograph of your choosing is printed directly onto a beautiful high quality pallet made from thick premium wood so that you can treasure it forever.

Keep your literary collection organized with a little humor by propping up your books using these T-Rex attack metal bookends. The clever design creates the illusion a ferocious T-Rex is chasing after two tasty human-sized morsels.

Look Morty, I’ve turned myself into a coffee mug. Boom, big reveal – it’s Coffee Mug Rick! This hilarious ceramic mug is designed with a dishwasher and microwave-safe graphic that creates the illusion you’re drinking from a coffee mug version of Rick Sanchez.
